- Keep the repo Node-only and dependency-light.
- Preserve the dp1-go-aligned module layout under `src/`.
- Prefer built-in Node APIs for JSON, crypto, and filesystem behavior.
- Keep documentation, workflows, and tests aligned with any exported API changes.
- Do not introduce browser-specific assumptions unless the request explicitly broadens the runtime.
